Class AbstractResourceService

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    com.google.common.util.concurrent.Service, Nameable, ResourceService

    public abstract class AbstractResourceService
extends AbstractGenericService<ResourceProvider,ResourceManager>
implements ResourceService
    An abstract implementation of ResourceService. This skeleton implementation provides an abstract builder mechanism to construct instances of extended classes. It holds resource provider and manager.
    Since:
    1.0
    Author:
    Pavol Zbell
